         <abstract id="aspace_46ca0aea395889b550ef950dc7122ddf">The papers consist of correspondence and printed matter relating primarily to Ralph McCallister's service as director and vice-president of the Chautauqua Institution (1944-1961). Major correspondents in the papers are Rebecca Richmond who was active in promoting Chautauqua activities and Alburn E. Skinner, a trustee.</abstract>
